湖北脑瘫儿之死：多方曾介入救助 父亲被隔离时想带其入院。
Death of a child with cerebral palsy in Hubei Province: Multiple parties intervened to help her father get hospitalized when he was isolated.
梁耀丹。
Liang Yaodan.
清流工作室                      。
Cleaning Studio.
